📝 Category 2: Ephemeral Storage Integration

   4. SessionCommit - Dehydrated ephemeral session
      Example: Game save with 42 vertices

   5. SliceCheckout - Slice checked out to ephemeral
      Example: Data borrowed by another session

   6. SliceReturn - Slice returned from ephemeral
      Example: Data returned after processing

📝 Category 3: Data Anchoring

   7. DataAnchor - Content-addressed data
      Example: PDF document (1MB)

   8. BraidCommit - Semantic attribution braid
      Example: Research paper attribution

📝 Category 4: Certificate Operations (NFT-like)

   9. CertificateMint - Create new certificate
      Example: Achievement certificate

   10. CertificateTransfer - Transfer ownership
       Example: Alice → Bob

   11. CertificateLoan - Temporary transfer
       Example: Bob loans to Alice for 1 hour

   12. CertificateReturn - Return loaned certificate
       Example: Alice returns to Bob

📝 Category 5: Slice Operations (Waypoints)

   13. SliceAnchor - Slice anchored at waypoint
       Example: Data snapshot at this spine

   14. SliceOperation - Operation on slice
       Example: Data transformation

   15. SliceDeparture - Slice leaves waypoint
       Example: Moving to next location

